headline: Linde Reports Third-Quarter 2025 Results
summary: WOKING, England, October 31, 2025--Linde plc (Nasdaq: LIN) today reported third-quarter 2025 net income of $1,929 million and diluted earnings per share of $4.09, up 24% and up 27%, respectively. Excluding Linde AG purchase accounting impacts and cost reduction program and other charges, adjusted net income was $1,987 million, up 5% versus prior year. Adjusted earnings per share was $4.21, 7% above prior year.
